 <class>requests_settings_ui</class>
 <widget class="QWidget" name="requests_settings_ui">
  <property name="geometry">
   <rect>
    <x>0</x>
    <y>0</y>
    <width>640</width>
    <height>480</height>
   </rect>
  </property>
  <property name="windowTitle">
   <string>Settings</string>
  </property>
  <property name="tabOrder" stdset="0">
   <number>2</number>
  </property>
  <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="main_layout">
   <property name="margin">
    <number>10</number>
   </property>
   <property name="spacing">
    <number>10</number>
   </property>
   <item>
    <widget class="QCheckBox" name="enable_checkbox">
     <property name="text">
      <string>Enable Requests support</string>
     </property>
    </widget>
   </item>
   <item>
    <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="fuzzy_layout">
     <item>
      <widget class="QLabel" name="fuzzy_threshold_label">
       <property name="text">
        <string>Fuzzy Match Threshold:</string>
       </property>
      </widget>
     </item>
     <item>
      <widget class="QSpinBox" name="fuzzy_threshold_spinbox">
       <property name="minimum">
        <number>50</number>
       </property>
       <property name="maximum">
        <number>100</number>
       </property>
       <property name="value">
        <number>85</number>
       </property>
       <property name="suffix">
        <string>%</string>
       </property>
       <property name="toolTip">
        <string>Minimum similarity score for fuzzy matching (50-100%). Higher values require closer matches.</string>
       </property>
      </widget>
     </item>
     <item>
      <spacer>
       <property name="orientation">
        <enum>Qt::Horizontal</enum>
       </property>
       <property name="sizeHint" stdset="0">
        <size>
         <width>40</width>
         <height>20</height>
        </size>
       </property>
      </spacer>
     </item>
    </layout>
   </item>
   <item>
    <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="klipy_layout">
     <item>
      <widget class="QLabel" name="klipy_key_label">
       <property name="text">
        <string>Klipy API Key:</string>
       </property>
      </widget>
     </item>
     <item>
      <widget class="QLineEdit" name="klipy_key_lineedit">
       <property name="placeholderText">
        <string>Enter Klipy API key for GifWords mode (optional)</string>
       </property>
       <property name="toolTip">
        <string>API key from Klipy (https://klipy.com/docs). Required for GifWords request mode.</string>
       </property>
      </widget>
     </item>
    </layout>
   </item>
   <item>
    <widget class="QTextBrowser" name="settings_infobox">
     <property name="sizePolicy">
      <sizepolicy hsizetype="Expanding" vsizetype="Expanding">
       <horstretch>0</horstretch>
       <verstretch>1</verstretch>
      </sizepolicy>
     </property>
     <property name="html">
      <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }
li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }
li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Request System Overview:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Fuzzy Matching:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;Request matching uses fuzzy search to handle typos and extra words. For example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;• &quot;play anything by nine inche nails please&quot; matches &quot;Nine Inch Nails&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;• &quot;somthing by the beatls&quot; matches &quot;The Beatles&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;Adjust the threshold to control sensitivity - higher values require closer matches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Request Processing Flow:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;1. User sends chat command or redeems channel points&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;2. System checks permissions and cooldowns (chat commands only)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;3. Request is processed based on the configured mode&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;4. Response is sent back to chat using the configured template&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;GIF APIs for GifWords:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;GifWords mode displays animated GIFs based on text keywords. A Klipy API key is required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;• &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Klipy&lt;/span&gt;: https://klipy.com/docs - Free API&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Next Steps:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;1. Configure your commands in the &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Commands&lt;/span&gt; tab&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;2. Set up Twitch integration in the &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Integration&lt;/span&gt; tab&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;3. Configure permissions and disable unwanted commands in the &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600&quot;&gt;Twitch Chat&lt;/span&gt; settings&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
     </property>
    </widget>
   </item>
  </layout>
 </widget>
